{"tid":1550764,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"以正視聽: 如果香港經濟出現衰退，香港警察要付最大責任。","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T13:26:38.000Z","uid":78947,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4458da78ac657c1219a043d5771308119cf7d3ae","tid":1550764,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59746670da5d5ee8e7c1e5e98009125b5a078c1","tid":1550764,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f75bd173350fe4a11b4af334da3bbc0e694ac272","tid":1550764,"uid":160247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:34:04.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 As we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 With eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 We shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 This perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 Determined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot; With hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"5a8c4bfb27f228f493aad45b8b02758a676d5a7f","tid":1550764,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb92d6c8285eafcb9f3fc68f0e6324116ae4fde1","tid":1550764,"uid":50386,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:17:43.000Z","msg":"淨係機場啲商戶都多謝機管局同警察啦<br />\n本來和你飛果幾日賺到笑<br />\n而家冇晒人幫襯,連等接機前去行下既客都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59db6b7a816814beebc78aeb20e702d53bdb8fba","tid":1550764,"uid":278434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:25:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1544490/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1544490/page/1</a><br />\nBNO轉BC, 平權聯署最後100米大直路！"},{"pid":"ab1a0814a4fa47ea0c1c93c43e608962b2d8055a","tid":1550764,"uid":314830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4458da78ac657c1219a043d5771308119cf7d3ae","tid":1550764,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:14:11.000Z","msg":"仲